ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Newfoundland and Labrador
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of NEWFOUNDLAND AND LABRADOR (1) the Hon. RAYMOND P. WHALEN from November 21 to December 2, 2017, inclusive; and (2) the Hon. B. Gale Welsh to be Administrator for the Government of Newfoundland and Labrador effective December 3, 2017.
